how to do it collectively

00:24:38.820 --> 00:24:40.950
in coordination.

00:24:40.950 --> 00:24:44.160
And that's true of
every blockchain

00:24:44.160 --> 00:24:45.540
that you can think about.

00:24:45.540 --> 00:24:48.600
Governance relates
to coordination

00:24:48.600 --> 00:24:51.920
